<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.3.10">
<l>peṟṟārā rāyiram pērāṉaip pērpāṭap</l>
<l>peṟṟāṉ kaliya ṉolicey tamiḻmālai</l>
<l>kaṟṟārō muṟṟula kāḷva rivaikēṭka</l>
<l>luṟṟārkku ṟutuya rillai yulakattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As to the ones who learn the garland of Tamil verse</l>
<l rend="indent">composed in the words of Kaliyaṉ,</l>
<l>He who gets to sing the names of the one</l>
<l rend="indent">with one-thousand names, they are never sated;</l>
<l>They will rule the whole world! For those who experience hearing these,</l>
<l>There will be no suffered sorrows in the world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
